In this statement, Donald J. Trump expresses his commitment to protecting the environment and natural resources of the United States. He acknowledges the importance of keeping air and water clean, preserving forests and open spaces, and protecting endangered species. Trump believes that economic growth can go hand in hand with environmental protection and is working towards reducing unnecessary burdens on workers and companies. He emphasizes the importance of rigorous science in understanding the environment and environmental risks, stating that it should be based on honest inquiry and robust debate rather than ideology. Trump concludes by expressing his hope that the nation can come together on Earth Day to appreciate the land they all love and call home.